data.description: This immaculate two-story home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, plus bar area in basement. Wood floors throughout the main level to include an office with french doors. Open floor plan, gourmet kitchen with granite counters, and stainless steel appliances. Cozy fireplace in Living room. Master bedroom suite has 5 pc bath and walk-in closet. Laundry room on main level. Finished basement has a spacious family room, game or play area, bar area, full bath, plus extra storage area. Central A/C for those hot Colorado Summers. Beautifully landscaped and the back yard is fully fenced. Close to parks, schools, trails, community recreation center with pools, fitness center, golf course, shops, restaurants, and military bases. Don't wait for a new build when this stunning home is move-in ready.
